Eat.

62
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,030
Don't like it?

63
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:35,520
Xiaozhou...

64
00:02:36,630 --> 00:02:37,080
I...

65
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,360
There's something I want to tell you.

66
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,910
Actually, I have something to tell you too.

67
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,080
You go first.

68
00:02:47,190 --> 00:02:48,030
You go first.

69
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,030
I...

70
00:02:52,710 --> 00:02:53,840
It's nothing really, just...

71
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,280
I feel a bit nervous.

72
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,630
