00:10:59,790 --> 00:11:01,120
That's not right, is it?

295
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:04,270
If you ask me, maybe just forget it.

296
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:05,910
Sorry.

297
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,320
