298
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:11,480
Want fish?

299
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,600
How much for this fish?

300
00:11:12,670 --> 00:11:14,390
It's cheap now, on sale. It's eighteen.

301
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:15,630
One kilo, please.

302
00:11:15,670 --> 00:11:16,000
Got it.

303
00:11:21,380 --> 00:11:21,900
Yes?

304
00:11:22,340 --> 00:11:22,780
Oh my.

305
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,360
Just when Chen Laifu

306
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,630
