307
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:26,360
then?

308
00:11:26,630 --> 00:11:27,790
His mom can't get covered.

309
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:28,910
We're back to square one again.

310
00:11:30,540 --> 00:11:30,900
Hey.

311
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:34,270
I remember one company's health plan

312
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:36,120
