313
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:38,600
Check TSI's system

314
00:11:38,910 --> 00:11:39,550
See if they do it.

315
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:42,630
Okay, I got it.

316
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:44,150
Don't just say "got it".

317
00:11:44,150 --> 00:11:44,870
Go check right now.

318
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:45,960
I need results immediately.

319
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:50,750
Hu Manli,
my mom's having surgery this afternoon.

320
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:52,320
Right!

321
00:11:53,150 --> 00:11:53,440
Then,

322
00:11:53,870 --> 00:11:54,670
give me your account info.

323
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,750
I'll log in to check, okay?

324
00:11:56,790 --> 00:11:57,510
Okay, hold on a sec.

325
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:58,440
Got it.

326
00:11:58,960 --> 00:11:59,270
Send it to me.

327
00:12:14,860 --> 00:12:16,860
[A little something to wish your mom good luck]

328
00:12:39,020 --> 00:12:40,860
[Insurance plans]

329
00:12:45,030 --> 00:12:47,320
Everwell Retirement Medical Insurance.

330
00:12:48,270 --> 00:12:48,750
Found it.

331
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,360
Everwell Retirement.

332
00:12:57,390 --> 00:12:59,240
Hello, Auntie? What's up?

333
00:13:01,300 --> 00:13:01,780
What?

334
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:03,910
Still can't reach him?

335
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,200
Professor Ding.

336
00:13:12,510 --> 00:13:13,270
Oh, you're here.

337
00:13:13,550 --> 00:13:15,390
Your phone was off,
couldn't contact you.

338
00:13:17,390 --> 00:13:18,200
What do you need?

339
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:20,510
Here's the situation.

340
00:13:20,910 --> 00:13:21,630
The summary for

341
00:13:21,630 --> 00:13:23,910
our department meeting
for the Party Committee is ready.

342
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:26,120
Professor Wang said you need to sign it.

343
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:30,000
Also, the department secretary needs

344
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,750
your final approval
on next week's lecture topics.

345
00:13:32,670 --> 00:13:33,080
Also,

346
00:13:33,390 --> 00:13:35,720
I've got two editorial replies pending

347
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:37,360
that need your review and confirmation.

348
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:38,670
Alright.

349
00:13:39,390 --> 00:13:40,320
By the way...

350
00:13:40,630 --> 00:13:42,000
Has Ms. Qiu contacted you?

351
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:44,080
No, why?

352
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:45,960
Just remember this.

353
00:13:46,510 --> 00:13:47,390
If she contacts you,

354
00:13:47,510 --> 00:13:48,120
tell her

355
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:50,150
I don't really want to see her lately.

356
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,510
Okay.

357
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:57,080
May I come in?

358
00:14:00,390 --> 00:14:00,870
You go ahead.

359
00:14:01,220 --> 00:14:01,660
Yes.

360
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:08,720
Have a seat.

361
00:14:09,670 --> 00:14:10,600
That's alright.

362
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:14,750
What? You needed something from me?

363
00:14:15,550 --> 00:14:16,600
Nothing from me.

364
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:17,720
But someone else needs you.

365
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:20,550
Why's your phone been off all this time?

366
00:14:23,510 --> 00:14:24,510
Just need some peace and quiet.

367
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:30,550
Your uncle and aunt
are here for medical treatment.

368
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:32,200
They've been
trying to reach you for days.

369
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:33,840
You should contact them immediately.

370
00:14:34,220 --> 00:14:35,020
Hm?

371
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:36,550
Give them a call.

372
00:14:37,500 --> 00:14:38,780
Oh, right.

373
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:44,720
It's switched off.

374
00:14:50,510 --> 00:14:53,080
Ding Zhiyuan,
now you're a big professor.

375
00:14:53,750 --> 00:14:55,750
Are you avoiding us poor relatives?

376
00:14:56,630 --> 00:14:57,080
No.

377
00:14:57,630 --> 00:14:59,120
I've just been very busy recently.

378
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:00,480
That's why I turned off my phone.

379
00:15:02,150 --> 00:15:03,150
You're here for medical treatment?

380
00:15:04,270 --> 00:15:04,550
Yes.

381
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:07,510
For your uncle's treatment, here.

382
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:08,960
Have some water, take a rest.

383
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:10,000
Thank you.

384
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:16,910
Where are you planning to go
for treatment?

385
00:15:19,030 --> 00:15:20,360
We should be asking you about this.

386
00:15:20,750 --> 00:15:21,270
Asking me?

387
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:23,510
What would we know about it?

388
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:25,120
We came all the way from out of town.

389
00:15:25,790 --> 00:15:27,120
Just tell us where to go for treatment.

390
00:15:27,270 --> 00:15:28,390
We'll go wherever you arrange.

391
00:15:29,910 --> 00:15:30,960
You want me to arrange it?

392
00:15:31,550 --> 00:15:32,840
But I don't know anything about this.

393
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:33,600
You...

394
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:35,240
You...

395
00:15:36,620 --> 00:15:37,460
Gosh!

396
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:41,270
Zhiyuan.

397
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:43,150
Actually,

398
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:45,630
your uncle's surgery

399
00:15:45,870 --> 00:15:47,670
could be done
at the provincial hospital.

400
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:49,030
It's not that difficult.

401
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:51,510
But we don't know anyone there.

402
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,630
We don't feel secure.

403
00:15:53,670 --> 00:15:55,270
After much deliberation,

404
00:15:55,390 --> 00:15:57,200
we decided to come to you.

405
00:15:57,600 --> 00:15:58,960
You're in Shanghai now.

406
00:15:59,270 --> 00:16:00,440
A famous professor

407
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:02,120
must have good connections

408
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:03,320
and knows lots of people.

409
00:16:03,510 --> 00:16:03,840
Right?

410
00:16:04,030 --> 00:16:05,120
You could arrange this for us.

411
00:16:07,550 --> 00:16:08,790
Why does it sound like

412
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:10,510
you don't want to help?

413
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:12,960
That's not what I meant.

414
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:15,670
I am a professor

415
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:17,670
but not at a medical school.

416
00:16:18,150 --> 00:16:18,670
Besides,

417
00:16:19,030 --> 00:16:20,480
I don't know any other doctors.

418
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,000
Oh my.

419
00:16:22,390 --> 00:16:24,360
What kind of talk is that?

420
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:26,390
Only medical school professors

421
00:16:26,390 --> 00:16:27,720
can know doctors?

422
00:16:27,870 --> 00:16:29,150
What kind of logic is that?

423
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,270
Anyway, let me tell you.

424
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:32,270
Your uncle and I

425
00:16:32,270 --> 00:16:33,750
came to you for help today.

426
00:16:34,150 --> 00:16:35,720
You've got to show your uncle respect.

427
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:38,910
This isn't about respect.

428
00:16:39,510 --> 00:16:40,960
Look how suddenly you came

429
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:41,910
without any notice.

430
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:44,000
How could I find someone on such short notice?

431
00:16:45,030 --> 00:16:45,670
What notice?

432
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:50,080
Coming to you is like coming home.

433
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:51,510
We treat you as family.

434
00:16:51,630 --> 00:16:52,270
Why give notice?

435
00:16:52,750 --> 00:16:53,750
Why give notice, I ask you?

436
00:16:54,630 --> 00:16:55,080
Zhiyuan.

437
00:16:58,120 --> 00:16:58,750
Actually,

438
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:01,510
we didn't mean to trouble you,

439
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:02,240
right?

440
00:17:02,750 --> 00:17:04,270
Before, we'd ask Manli.

441
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:05,590
She handled everything for us.

442
00:17:06,030 --> 00:17:08,310
Whenever Manli took us to see doctors,

443
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:09,920
she always knew someone and

444
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:12,200
arranged everything perfectly.

445
00:17:12,240 --> 00:17:13,510
We never had to worry at all.

446
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:14,310
But now,

447
00:17:14,680 --> 00:17:16,310
you two have broken up.

448
00:17:16,350 --> 00:17:16,790
Right?

449
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:18,830
Then it's not appropriate
to contact her.

450
00:17:19,310 --> 00:17:20,110
And you!

451
00:17:20,110 --> 00:17:21,830
Why did you break up for no reason?

452
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:23,070
What a mess!

453
00:17:23,310 --> 00:17:24,000
Auntie.

454
00:17:24,350 --> 00:17:25,920
Can we not talk about the breakup?

455
00:17:26,270 --> 00:17:27,160
Fine, won't mention it.

456
00:17:28,030 --> 00:17:28,720
Okay.

457
00:17:29,270 --> 00:17:31,880
Won't mention Professor Ding's breakup.

458
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:33,440
I've finally figured it out.

459
00:17:34,110 --> 00:17:34,550
You...

460
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:37,640
He's nothing without Manli!

461
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:38,880
He can't accomplish anything!

462
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:39,960
Let's pack up.

463
00:17:39,960 --> 00:17:40,880
Go home!

464
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:41,440
Don't.

465
00:17:41,440 --> 00:17:42,720
We can't trouble Professor Ding!

466
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:43,270
- Uncle. - No.

467
00:17:43,270 --> 00:17:43,880
- Don't be mad. -Go!

468
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:45,270
Seeing a doctor?

469
00:17:45,310 --> 00:17:46,000
That's simple.

470
00:17:46,960 --> 00:17:48,720
Here's what we'll do.

471
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:49,920
Let's go to the hospital.

472
00:17:50,270 --> 00:17:51,200
If it's serious,

473
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:52,880
we'll figure something out.

474
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:54,920
We can visit a few hospitals.

475
00:17:55,270 --> 00:17:56,070
Listen to more doctors.

476
00:17:56,070 --> 00:17:56,790
That's good, no?

477
00:18:00,350 --> 00:18:00,680
Alright.

478
00:18:01,160 --> 00:18:01,720
Well.

479
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,240
We'll follow your arrangements.

480
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:09,000
Don't get angry so easily.

481
00:18:12,550 --> 00:18:13,030
Okay.

482
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:14,920
Excuse me, may I cut in line?

483
00:18:17,030 --> 00:18:18,000
Thank you.

484
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:20,480
Gosh, look!

485
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:22,590
He's already let several cut in.

486
00:18:23,590 --> 00:18:25,030
When will we ever get our turn?

487
00:18:26,350 --> 00:18:27,680
I'll go relieve him. I'll queue up.

488
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:30,510
Zhiyuan.

489
00:18:31,110 --> 00:18:32,550
Go rest a while, I'll queue.

490
00:18:33,270 --> 00:18:34,240
Go ahead, go on.

491
00:18:37,440 --> 00:18:39,160
There's quite a queue here.

492
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:46,200
Zhiyuan.

493
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:47,960
I

494
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:49,920
need to talk with you.

495
00:18:51,310 --> 00:18:52,200
Why exactly

496
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:54,590
did you separate?

497
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:59,240
Can we change the subject?

498
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:05,200
You can't just

499
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:07,750
break up your marriage over

500
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:09,000
trivial matters.

501
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:11,550
Think about your child.

502
00:19:13,200 --> 00:19:14,270
Your Dingding

503
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:17,550
is such a lovely boy.

504
00:19:18,030 --> 00:19:19,200
Think about him.

505
00:19:19,550 --> 00:19:20,160
How about this?

506
00:19:20,310 --> 00:19:21,350
Later I'll have your aunt

507
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:22,790
talk to Manli.

508
00:19:22,880 --> 00:19:23,680
Talk it over.

509
00:19:24,030 --> 00:19:25,790
You two should remarry.

510
00:19:26,070 --> 00:19:26,480
Alright?

511
00:19:26,790 --> 00:19:28,720
Don't bother yourself.

512
00:19:29,310 --> 00:19:30,000
Actually...

513
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:34,830
Actually, I've been seeing someone else.

514
00:19:36,510 --> 00:19:36,960
What?!

515
00:19:38,510 --> 00:19:39,270
About this matter,

516
00:19:39,350 --> 00:19:40,270
I was in the wrong.

517
00:19:41,480 --> 00:19:42,880
But between me and Manli

518
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:44,830
there's also

519
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:46,920
incompatible personalities.

520
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:48,110
We just can't go on anymore.

521
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:54,640
You're being foolish!

522
00:19:55,110 --> 00:19:55,960
Manli

523
00:19:56,480 --> 00:19:57,070
treats you well,

524
00:19:57,680 --> 00:19:58,480
treats the kid well, and

525
00:19:58,880 --> 00:19:59,680
treats your parents well.

526
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:01,270
She treats us well too!

527
00:20:01,590 --> 00:20:02,350
You mustn't let

528
00:20:02,590 --> 00:20:04,000
those sly women bewitch you!

529
00:20:04,790 --> 00:20:07,510
Uncle, it's not what you imagine.

530
00:20:08,510 --> 00:20:10,750
My partner is a good person, very gentle.

531
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:12,350
She's even a big company's CEO.

532
00:20:13,640 --> 00:20:14,310
Besides,

533
00:20:14,720 --> 00:20:16,480
I'm already in my forties.

534
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:19,070
I know what I'm doing.

535
00:20:20,740 --> 00:20:21,780
Hey!

536
00:20:22,510 --> 00:20:24,440
There's still over eighty ahead.

537
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:27,030
How long are we going to wait here?

538
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:29,110
Zhiyuan, hurry and find someone to help.

539
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:31,830
Big hospitals are always this

540
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:32,480
crowded.

541
00:20:32,790 --> 00:20:34,160
If we need to queue, then we'll queue.

542
00:20:34,550 --> 00:20:35,680
No specialist appointments left.

543
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:36,440
What should we do?

544
00:20:36,550 --> 00:20:37,070
No more left?

545
00:20:37,070 --> 00:20:37,880
None at all.

546
00:20:38,510 --> 00:20:38,830
Well...

547
00:20:39,030 --> 00:20:40,000
Let's go line up first.

548
00:20:40,960 --> 00:20:41,240
Go.

549
00:20:41,270 --> 00:20:42,270
I... I'll go queue too?

550
00:20:42,350 --> 00:20:43,000
Let's queue up.

551
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:44,920
Go wait outside the consultation room.

552
00:20:44,920 --> 00:20:45,200
Okay.

553
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:46,160
Which way do we go?

554
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:48,240
Straight ahead, then turn right.

555
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:49,680
Are you sure?

556
00:20:49,750 --> 00:20:50,550
Yes, it's over there.

557
00:21:32,830 --> 00:21:33,400
Don't worry.

558
00:21:33,920 --> 00:21:34,550
It'll be fine.

559
00:22:03,440 --> 00:22:04,070
Zhiyuan...

560
00:22:05,750 --> 00:22:07,070
He looks too young.

561
00:22:07,550 --> 00:22:09,000
Not even thirty yet.

562
00:22:09,590 --> 00:22:10,200
Is he qualified?

563
00:22:11,440 --> 00:22:13,680
Let's hear what the doctor says first.

564
00:22:14,310 --> 00:22:14,830
Don't worry.

565
00:22:17,350 --> 00:22:18,590
I'll order a CT scan for you.

566
00:22:18,590 --> 00:22:19,310
Go get it done.

567
00:22:20,270 --> 00:22:22,110
We've already had it done at the provincial hospital.

568
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:22,590
Right.

569
00:22:22,680 --> 00:22:24,240
See, this is a CT scan right here.

570
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:25,960
This was done at your local hospital.

571
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:26,920
Might not be accurate.

572
00:22:27,310 --> 00:22:28,240
If you want our diagnosis,

573
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:28,880
you need to redo it.

574
00:22:29,880 --> 00:22:30,240
Doctor,

575
00:22:30,790 --> 00:22:31,880
before we came here,

576
00:22:31,880 --> 00:22:34,000
we already looked it up online.

577
00:22:34,240 --> 00:22:35,110
For my condition,

578
00:22:35,720 --> 00:22:37,110
there's no need for so many tests.

579
00:22:37,270 --> 00:22:38,510
Just operate on me.

580
00:22:40,160 --> 00:22:41,000
You checked online.

581
00:22:41,750 --> 00:22:44,070
Sir, if internet could cure illnesses,
what do we

582
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:45,510
need hospitals for?

583
00:22:45,790 --> 00:22:46,750
What would doctors be for?

584
00:22:47,310 --> 00:22:48,110
How dare you!

585
00:22:48,270 --> 00:22:48,960
Young man,

586
00:22:49,160 --> 00:22:50,550
are you just trying to take our money?

